Subject: [PATCH] PCI/VPD: Remove sysfs accessor size checking dead code
MIME-Version: 1.0
Git-commit: 26c0cf2a603d4ebf00d8c1baf714763fca31dba4
Patch-mainline: v5.13-rc1
References: bsn#92
Modified-by-SEL: No

Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
